Huawei has unveiled its Black Friday 2020 deals, which offer big discounts on devices from its online store. The sale will go live at 19:00 on 25 November 2020 and will include flash sales as well as the chance to win a selection of Huawei hardware. Customers who act quickly after the sale begins can get a Huawei P40 Pro+, Watch GT 2 Pro, and MateBook D14 – all for only R4,999. Stock on this offer will be limited and it is expected to sell out quickly. Click here to visit the Huawei Online Store Huawei is also offering significant discounts across a range of smartphones, routers, laptops, and wearables. Additionally, visitors can enter a lucky draw competition, which puts them in line to win prizes valued at up to R28,999. Users can sign up on the Huawei website to receive notifications regarding the sale as well as enter for a chance to win a P40 Pro, P Smart S, or FreeLace earphones. A selection of Huawei’s Black Friday deals, which are set to go live on 25 November, are listed below. <img class="size-full wp-image-451278 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-451280 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-451282 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/upl